<http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4331927>
    bibo:endPage "289" ;
    bibo:journal "Insect Systematics & Evolution" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2009-01-01" ;
    bibo:startPage "253" ;
    bibo:volume "40" ;
    dc:creator "Dikow, Torsten; Bayless, Keith M." ;
    dc:date "2009" ;
    dc:title "Taxonomic revision of the genus Schildia Aldrich, 1923 (Diptera: Asilidae: Leptogastrinae) with the description of new extant and extinct species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3983033>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3983041>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3983039> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3983033>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Map of the world with extant and extinct distribution of Schildia indicated with solid circles. Note the restricted Old World distribution in Madagascar and Malaysia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3983033/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3983041>
    dc:description "Figs 13–24. Male terminalia of Schildia species with gonostyli (dark grey) and lateral processes of gonostyli (light grey) shaded in lateral views. (13–15) S. adina sp.n.: 13, lateral; 14, dorsal; 15, ventral. (16–18) S. gracillima: 16, lateral; 17, dorsal; 18, ventral. (19–21) S. guatemalae: 19, lateral; 20, dorsal; 21, ventral. (22–24) S. jamaicensis: 22, lateral; 23, dorsal; 24, ventral. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3983041/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3983039>
    dc:description "Figs 9–12. Photographs of extinct and extant species of Schildia. (9) †Schildia martini sp.n. (holotype, AMNH Luzzi); (10) †Schildia martini sp.n. (paratype, AMNH DR-V-7); (11) Schildia adina sp.n. preserved in Malagasy copal (Coll. Stuke). (12) Schildia fragilis (USNM, Peru).Scale bars = 1 mm.This figure is published in colour in the online edition that can be accessed via http://www.brill.nl/ise" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3983039/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

